<!-- Tab: About -->
<div class="tab-panel hidden lg:block" id="tab-about">
<div id="description" class="about-panel">
<h2 class="about-heading">About the Equivalent Arch Clearance Calculator</h2>
<p class="mb-4">The equivalent arch clearance calculator allows you to compare a specified wheel against other wheel sizes with the same arch clearance.</p>
<p class="mb-4">Once you have entered the wheel specification into the form on the left, the calculator will display the equivalent offset of wheels in various widths.</p>
<p class="mb-4">For example, you can calculate that a 9.5J et12 wheel would have the same arch clearance as an 8J et-7 wheel.</p>
<p><a href="javascript:switchTab('tab-calculator'); calculator.demo('offset-comparison', 0);" class="about-link">Click for a demo!</a></p>
